hopobject.body: The Cosmic Board is a richly featured and community-supported development platform for engineers to immediately develop applications with Linux, WinCE & Android.The Cosmic Board concept is unique from any other community-supported board because it's much more than a low cost hobbyist tool. At the center of the Cosmic Board is an industrial rated, production-ready, System on Module (SOM). By starting with a SOM-based solution, developers are much closer to product than they imagine. It's possible to have first article prototypes ready in weeks, not months! Sounds out of this world, doesn't it?
